name: Dark Flow Project File
summary: Learn about .DFK files and view a list of programs that open them.

content: A single Dark Flow project can be built for multiple platforms, including Microsoft Windows, the Web (as plugin-less Web games), and for console systems such as the Nintendo Wii, Sony PSP, and Microsoft Xbox.
Dark Flow follows DS Game Maker as Invisionsoft's next generation game development software. DS Game Maker is used for developing Nintendo DS games.
NOTE: Dark Flow is no longer developed.
